{"tid":790960,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"十姑娘何婉琪病逝享年95歲　料掀百億爭產戰","createTime":"2018-08-23T11:49:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-24T06:59:20.000Z","uid":48083,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6e133889eb0b3a7747fc74699e53c9739f8a834e","tid":790960,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T11:49:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/23/194916_9ea71d6de8c3441f8037c88b5b46f9fa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F23%2F194916_9ea71d6de8c3441f8037c88b5b46f9fa.png&h=28bf4363&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n賭王何鴻燊胞妹十姑娘何婉琪早前病逝，享年95歲。由於消息一直被封鎖，她於6月5日養和醫院病逝，至近日才為人知曉。十姑娘生前一直住在養和養病，嚴禁探望，而她死後安葬在摩星嶺的昭遠墳場。十姑娘發言人游小姐亦證實消息。 <br />\n<br />\n而十姑娘的大女麥慧貞亦證實母親死訊。由於十姑娘擁有澳娛價值約五十億股份的滿威利基金會，所以有親屬擔心會引起百億遺產爭奪戰。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180823/mobile/bkn-20180823161903780-0823_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180823%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180823161903780-0823_00862_001.html&d=9KtZC7Xczbv2fjYgGjHB7b%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=a3a42d96\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180823/mobile/bkn-20180823161903780-0823_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"345f47fdcf74dfbb1adc3f61df0d9273cf014d04","tid":790960,"uid":86756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T11:51:06.000Z","msg":"幾時到賀新<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c33c5173b666238d1add206e2c9cd19fe08c7a2e","tid":790960,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"345f47fdcf74dfbb1adc3f61df0d9273cf014d04","tid":790960,"uid":86756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T11:51:06.000Z","msg":"幾時到賀新<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T11:52:31.000Z","msg":"隨時封鎖緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma